## Problem Statement
Many people cannot easily understand whether their body weight is healthy or not. Without a proper calculation method, they may end up assuming they are healthy or unhealthy. The BMI system solves this by giving a standard measurable value.

## Scope of the Project
The project calculates BMI based on user input and categorizes users as Underweight, Normal, Overweight, or Obese. It is useful for students, doctors, gym trainers, fitness enthusiasts, and health apps.

## Target Users
- Students
- Gym and fitness members
- Dieticians and doctors
- Health mobile app users

## High-Level Features
- Accept height and weight input
- Calculate BMI using the standard formula
- Display BMI value and category
- Handle incorrect input gracefully
